Aether — Cross-platform Agent SDK
===================================

This product includes software developed by Nous Research:

  Hermes Agent (https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent)
  Copyright (c) 2025 Nous Research
  Licensed under the MIT License

Aether is a clean Rust reimplementation of the Hermes Agent architecture,
designed for cross-platform deployment (Android, iOS, Windows, macOS, Linux, Web).
The architecture, agent loop design, memory system, skill format, and learning
loop concepts are derived from Hermes Agent, but all code is independently
written in Rust.

Portions of this product's design and behavior are inspired by Hermes Agent's
source code (Python), reviewed for architectural understanding and reimplemented
in Rust with platform-native idioms.

